{"tid":268394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【阿仔被派青衣】雙非家長不滿鬧港人：國民關心香港 你們不關心國民","createTime":"2017-06-03T04:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T03:40:12.000Z","uid":609,"like":3,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cf4de7b2361fa5cfebb7e8156c01fc351aff8284","tid":268394,"uid":609,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T04:38:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_517176_0&amp;i=20170603\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_517176_0%26i%3D20170603&d=knWvGpRPpceUlwMg7f3hGMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ea7465c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_517176_0%26i%3D20170603&h=96613af3\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_517176_0&amp;i=20170603</a><br />\n<br />\n小一派位今日公布結果。除了本地家長，有一眾雙非學童家長亦到派位中心等候消息。 <br />\n<br />\n有家長對結果感到不滿，形容結果「搞甚麼鬼」，又指<span style=\"color: red;\">「全國人民關心香港，香港不關心全國人民」</span> <br />\n<br />\n居住羅湖的李先生對結果表示失望，形容結果令自己很難接受。他表示小朋友在香港出生，一定要入讀香港學校，又指會繼續叩門，希望「叩到開為止」，相信政府不會放棄兒子。 <br />\n<br />\n他表示，妻子為了兒子的小一派位，這幾個月準備很多資料，又會找其他家長作交流，原本亦打算讓兒子住在香港親戚在大埔的房子。 <br />\n<br />\n李女士的子女則被派到青衣區小學，認為地點遙遠，希望該學校會為孩子安排跨境校車接送服務。"},{"pid":"39d881f04bff4846a172d7928c7572aba0cd909a","tid":268394,"uid":6604,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T04:39:48.000Z","msg":"死返支那啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddba728313177706e115fd1591928f77f4d7fca","tid":268394,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T04:41:04.000Z","msg":"躝返去支那啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823270f4e8414d4617f6228c8445057cffacfa28","tid":268394,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T04:41:38.000Z","msg":"支那蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a23838c1e736c97c746548e2b6f0ee9b4203e1